text: The Alfa Romeo 145 is a car produced by Alfa Romeo. It replaced the Alfa Romeo 33 in 1994, and were replaced by the Alfa Romeo 147 in 2000. == Engines == === Petrol === * 1.4 66 kW (90 hp) * 1.4 Twin Spark 16V 76 kW (103 hp) * 1.6 76 kW (103 hp) * 1.6 Twin Spark 16V 88 kW (120 hp) * 1.7 16V 95 kW (129 hp) * 1.8 Twin Spark 16V 103 kW (140 hp) and 106 kW (144 hp) * 2.0 Quadrifogilo 110 kW (150 hp) and 114 kW (155 hp) === Diesel === * 1.9 JTD 77 kW (105 hp) * 2.0 TD 66 kW (90 hp) 145 Category:1990s automobiles Category:2000s automobiles
